       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. INIT-DB.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT ACCOUNT-FILE ASSIGN TO 'ACCOUNTS.DAT'
               ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  ACCOUNT-FILE.
       01 ACCOUNT-REC.
          05 REC-ACC-NUMBER   PIC 9(10).
          05 REC-ACC-NAME     PIC X(30).
          05 REC-ACC-BALANCE  PIC S9(13)V99.
          05 REC-ACC-STATUS   PIC X(1).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-EOF-FLAG         PIC X         VALUE 'N'.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
           OPEN OUTPUT ACCOUNT-FILE.

           MOVE 1000000001 TO REC-ACC-NUMBER.
           MOVE 'JOHN DOE' TO REC-ACC-NAME.
           MOVE 5000.00 TO REC-ACC-BALANCE.
           MOVE 'A' TO REC-ACC-STATUS.
           WRITE ACCOUNT-REC.

           MOVE 1000000002 TO REC-ACC-NUMBER.
           MOVE 'JANE SMITH' TO REC-ACC-NAME.
           MOVE 12500.50 TO REC-ACC-BALANCE.
           MOVE 'A' TO REC-ACC-STATUS.
           WRITE ACCOUNT-REC.

           MOVE 1000000003 TO REC-ACC-NUMBER.
           MOVE 'BOB JOHNSON' TO REC-ACC-NAME.
           MOVE 100.00 TO REC-ACC-BALANCE.
           MOVE 'A' TO REC-ACC-STATUS.
           WRITE ACCOUNT-REC.

           CLOSE ACCOUNT-FILE.
           DISPLAY 'Database initialized.'.
           STOP RUN.
